"2026-03-31 15:15", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=862980539,45974302,3203]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60925933]ywlight2468[/uid] (2026-03-31 15:11):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，这一波储能没涨还被砸晕了，长线仓位还在么？[/quote]<br/>我啥时候长线有储能了？我只有做了T的电池", "lou": 1645, "content_length": 44, "reply_to": 862980539, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774941350}, {"pid": 862998234, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 18, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-31 17:25", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=862997840,45974302,3209]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=34145414]幸运的兔首[/uid] (2026-03-31 17:22):[/b]<br/><br/>之前说过3900上下50点的绞肉机，上50基本兑现，下50还差40个点[/quote]<br/>你看看27号的最低点[s:ac:哭笑]", "lou": 1646, "content_length": 21, "reply_to": 862997840, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774949150}, {"pid": 863003313, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 63, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-31 18:10", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我艹   XXX  XXXXX<br/>一个月中三个减持的我也是衰到家了", "lou": 1647, "content_length": 44, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774951848}, {"pid": 863007093, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 17, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-31 18:49", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863006897,45974302,3211]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60916468]灰兔尾[/uid] (2026-03-31 18:47):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，其实我一直以为机构做票的时候会和控股股东有联系，减持意向之类的消息会提前拿到，现在看来好像不是这样啊[/quote]<br/>除非老鼠仓 不然一般这种1%-3%的减持不会传播出去的。犯法的", "lou": 1648, "content_length": 60, "reply_to": 863006897, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1774954167}, {"pid": 863024888, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 35, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-31 22:23", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我下午有没有说明天大概率收红[s:ac:茶]<br/>希望美股今晚不要跳太多水就行", "lou": 1649, "content_length": 54, "from_client": "8 Android", "postdatetimestamp": 1774967002}, {"pid": 863026471, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 16, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-31 22:42", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863025206,45974302,3216]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=63219410]麦宝老爹[/uid] (2026-03-31 22:27):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，阴暗电源这个业绩，会不会带崩新能源风光储这条线啊？[s:ac:羡慕](上游成本上涨那么快)[/quote]<br/><br/>会吧 本来这条线做的就不是业绩 做的是战争能源替代，现在TACO预期，那叠加业绩利空，应该会有一次板块级别的杀恐慌盘才对 不然不会有下一波的上涨的", "lou": 1650, "content_length": 141, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 863025206, "postdatetimestamp": 1774968165}, {"pid": 863026885, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 17, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-31 22:48", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863026623,45974302,3217]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=2395594]枫叶那个落尘`[/uid] (2026-03-31 22:44):[/b]<br/><br/>所以狼大,,下午你说的低点 快点告诉我们吧[/quote]<br/><br/>你们听不懂的 把我前面那些提前预判多看看 先把大级别看懂再说日内吧", "lou": 1651, "content_length": 67, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 863026623, "postdatetimestamp": 1774968483}, {"pid": 863029494, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 18, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-31 23:20", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863027981,45974302,3218]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65607701]multporn[/uid] (2026-03-31 23:01):[/b]<br/><br/>海外消息面目前没人信美国撤军的，越来越多迹象表明美国准备上地面部队，你们计提战争结束的我觉得不要太乐观。[s:ac:哭笑][/quote]<br/><br/>他撤不撤都不会扩大化战争<br/>最简单的就是看海峡的船有没有跑路就行了<br/>现在进行的是谈判博弈，争取最后最大利益", "lou": 1652, "content_length": 105, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 863027981, "postdatetimestamp": 1774970450}, {"pid": 863030023, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 34, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-31 23:28", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "你们可能还是把目光局限在美国的目标是伊朗这种表象上，大家回想一下俄乌，最后是谁买单<br/>是欧公子啊<br/>这波是谁？当然是中东那些产油国大户，欧佩克前面还说要增产，你看他们现在是不是连空油桶都没了，这才是川普的真正目的啊", "lou": 1653, "content_length": 206, "from_client": "8 Android", "postdatetimestamp": 1774970884}, {"pid": 863052888, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 35, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-01 08:59", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[s:ac:茶]问题不大 现在就看能不能过缺口 和缺口上方的量能表现了<br/>整体思路不会有什么变化<br/>接下来就是交易TACO 所以这两天提前和你们说就是没人信我<br/>还有人在战争板块么", "lou": 1654, "content_length": 140, "from_client": "8 Android", "postdatetimestamp": 1775005175}, {"pid": 863053370, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 11, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-01 09:02", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863053058,45974302,3223]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=62242910]十香虞[/uid] (2026-04-01 09:00):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，新能源算战争板块么？[s:ac:瞎][/quote]<br/><br/>新能源这块你要分哪个细分 光伏储能新能车电池电网电力锂矿等等… 你说个新能源鬼才知道怎么说", "lou": 1655, "content_length": 91, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 863053058, "postdatetimestamp": 1775005366}, {"pid": 863053916, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 37, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-01 09:06", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我没有你们那么乐观噢 我就还是原来的思路 大A需要真金白银才能结束下跌行情<br/>目前是什么情况我也不用多说了 不排除有新的大资金进来把需要高抛的资金全吃了然后带市场上去  但是这得出现了才行啊。。。", "lou": 1656, "content_length": 181, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775005585}, {"pid": 863053984, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 17, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-01 09:06", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863053174,45974302,3223]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=64942487]答卷人[/uid] (2026-04-01 09:01):[/b]<br/><br/>老哥们情绪这么火热，推荐点T+0的让大家套套利，比如港股创新药etf，还有其他的吗 哥哥们推荐一手 急急急急[/quote]<br/>就这个 不用考虑别的 特别是港股券商ETF", "lou": 1657, "content_length": 40, "reply_to": 863053174, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775005613}, {"pid": 863054153, "fid": 7